{"hash":"4e091c9ca5d5185c044904119c48302008eedf36","data":{"post":{"id":"28fd871b43f53d7dbb647aa7dfe019e1","category":"기타","sub_category":"","title":"개발자 로드맵 2021","series_name":"","series_num":0,"content":"<p>2021년 버전이 새로 업데이트 되어 포스팅해본다.</p>\n<p>아직 한글버전은 준비되지 않은 것 같다.</p>\n<p>Backend는 변경점이 거의 없고, Devops에는 컨테이너쪽에 내용이 추가되었다.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"백엔드-개발자\"><a href=\"#%EB%B0%B1%EC%97%94%EB%93%9C-%EA%B0%9C%EB%B0%9C%EC%9E%90\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>백엔드 개발자</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.notion.so/image/https%3A%2F%2Fs3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com%2Fsecure.notion-static.com%2Fe108c347-11cb-403b-b811-844743e16283%2Fbackend.png?table=block&#x26;id=b9286018-5a02-4deb-9556-b0e96b806e23&#x26;width=2580&#x26;userId=038a9d8a-4e75-4deb-a374-ed6ff93980c6&#x26;cache=v2\"></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"데브옵스-개발자\"><a href=\"#%EB%8D%B0%EB%B8%8C%EC%98%B5%EC%8A%A4-%EA%B0%9C%EB%B0%9C%EC%9E%90\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>데브옵스 개발자</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.notion.so/image/https%3A%2F%2Fs3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com%2Fsecure.notion-static.com%2F8e20a241-5b2d-4742-87a0-e25c32c074fc%2Fdevops.png?table=block&#x26;id=7ea1d021-fac9-4a0a-804d-3118ad788878&#x26;width=2580&#x26;userId=038a9d8a-4e75-4deb-a374-ed6ff93980c6&#x26;cache=v2\"></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"reference\"><a href=\"#reference\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Reference</h2>\n<span class=\"reference\">\n<p><a href=\"https://roadmap.sh/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Developer Roadmaps</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/kamranahmedse/developer-roadmap\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Github</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/devJang/developer-roadmap\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Github: Korean</a></p>\n</span>\n","tags":[{"title":"개발자","path":"/tag/%EA%B0%9C%EB%B0%9C%EC%9E%90/"},{"title":"로드맵","path":"/tag/%EB%A1%9C%EB%93%9C%EB%A7%B5/"},{"title":"백엔드",